eNCA's Faith Mangope discusses this with Limpopo Health MEC, Phophi Ramathuba. Courtesy #DStv403 POLOKWANE - Limpopo Health faces medical negligence claims to the value of R14-billion. The Vhembe district has the highest number of claims at 500 but the department says some of the complaints are brought by unscrupulous people for money. READ: Discovery Health defends claiming funds from doctors Limpopo Health MEC, Phophi Ramathuba, says there is a plan and they are looking into all the cases